Mintlayer will support several main ways to interact with the chain and perform "normal interactions".

A web wallet, a mobile wallet, a command line interface and access through RPCs.

- gen key pair
- gen new seed
- get key pair from seed
- get pk from sk
- get derived keys
- get address from sk
- save keys locally
- delete keys
- stake
- send tx
- check from rx
- create token
- sign a tx
